<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مُحَمَّدٍ هُوَ الْجُعْفِيُّ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6844">وَهْبُ بْنُ جَرِيرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7060">وَأَبِي التَّيَّاحِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«بُعِثْتُ وَالسَّاعَةَ كَهَاتَيْنِ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>